summary: Adds \"No High Collision\" versions of the walls in Whiterun.  This was done for Open Cities Skyrim, and I\'m making it a resource.
descriptionHtml:
==========================================================
Whiterun Walls Collision Resources               by jonwd7

v1.0 (Initial Release)                           7/21/2012
==========================================================

 This was done by request and fixes the high collision on
the walls in Whiterun which did not already have \"no high
collision\" versions.

 There are 9 included statics so far. I have appended
\"nohighcoll\" to the filenames. These should NOT replace
the vanilla meshes for many reasons. So, please, for your
mods, create new statics in the CK for these files. You
can name them whatever you want, as long as they do not
overwrite the vanilla meshes.

 \"Nohighcoll\" versions are included in this resource for:
 
 `````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrstairswater01
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallcurve30up128a
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallcurve30up128
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallcurve45
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallcurve45up
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallcurve60
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallstrup128
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwalltierdivide01
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwalltowercap01
 ________________________________________________________

 More will be added if necessary.

 Please note that the vanilla game includes three meshes
with \"nohighcol(l)\" versions. These are:

 `````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallcap01nohighcol
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallstr01nohighcoll
| meshes\\architecture\\whiterun\\wrwallstrup128shift128nohighcol
 ________________________________________________________
